<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mḥbtk yạ rby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mḥbtk yạ rby bdt bsẖkl ʿjyb
 ạ̹zạy ạ̹nt bjlạlk tfdyny ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 ạlqrạr- lmạ lqytny fy kẖṭạyạya gẖrqạn wdạ kạn
 ḥạly
 mạhạnsẖ ʿlyk ạ̉nạ ạ̉hlk wdfʿt ạltmn ạlgẖạly
 ḍḥyt wmt bdạly
 2- mḥbtk yạ rby mạ sẖft lyhạ nẓyr
 mḥbẗ lạ tsqṭ ạ̉bdaⁿạ mạfyhạsẖ ạ̉bdaⁿạ tgẖyyr
 3- mḥbtk yạ rby mạyḥdhạsẖ mqyạs
 fy ʿẓmthạ wkmạlhạ tsẖml ạ̉sr ạlnạs</lyrics>
<author>ṣfạʾ ṣbḥy̱, nḥmyạ wdyʿ</author>
<hymn_number>9916</hymn_number>
</song>